General.Name: MEDirect Latino Inc
General.Description: MEDirect Latino, Inc. provides direct-to-consumer medical products to the Hispanic community in the United States and Puerto Rico. It supplies diabetic diagnostic testing supplies, and other products, including heating pads, seat lifts, and walking assistance devices. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Pompano Beach, Florida.
General.Address: 2101 West Atlantic Boulevard, Pompano Beach, FL, United States, 33069
